I'd give a choice of [Painter's Servant](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Painter's Servant), [Grindstone](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grindstone), [Argivian Restoration](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Argivian Restoration) and [Tinker](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tinker), if you've got at least one other artifact (probably one that gives mana) on the battlefield.


@Tommy9898: [Crucible of Worlds](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Crucible of Worlds) and [Academy Ruins](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Academy Ruins) to the graveyard, [Mindslaver](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mindslaver) and Gifts Ungiven to the hand. These selections delay your opponent the most, by probably two or three turns.


